He was one of the founding members of the People's Republic, senior official

19
00:01:25,820 --> 00:01:28,360
in the first decade of the People's Republic.

20
00:01:28,360 --> 00:01:32,620
What can you tell us about his background and his accomplishments

21
00:01:32,620 --> 00:01:36,710
and challenges in the formative decade, the 1950s?

22
00:01:36,710 --> 00:01:39,290
He had an extraordinarily rich background.

23
00:01:39,290 --> 00:01:43,680
He was born in 1904, spent five years in France in the '20s.

24
00:01:43,680 --> 00:01:48,310
He spent one year in the Soviet Union, '26-'27.

25
00:01:48,310 --> 00:01:50,790
He had been 12 years in the army.

26
00:01:50,790 --> 00:01:52,540
He had done local government.

27
00:01:52,540 --> 00:01:54,900
He had fought as a guerrilla fighter.

28
00:01:54,900 --> 00:01:58,280
He was a front commander for 500,000 troops in then,

29
00:01:58,280 --> 00:02:01,900
perhaps the most decisive battle of the country.

30
00:02:01,900 --> 00:02:06,300
