34
00:02:15,840 --> 00:02:19,430
So he'd had local experience in directing land reform,

35
00:02:19,430 --> 00:02:23,070
and carrying out the initial establishment of power.

36
00:02:23,070 --> 00:02:28,010
So when he came to Beijing, he was a leader already in the government.

37
00:02:28,010 --> 00:02:32,070
